    "en": {
      "title": "A trader is missing in Kandy",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A complaint has been lodged at the Peradanai Police Station by the wife of the missing man who has been missing for two days, who ran a business in front of the Peradanai Uthita Park.",
        "The 47-year-old man is also said to be a staunch supporter of Kandy-based politician Mahindananda Aluthkamake.",
        "The police said that the search for the missing person is going on and two murder cases filed against the person will be taken up for hearing next month."
      ],
